  <name>Flex Player</name>
  <summary>A modern, native media player for Plex</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>Flex Player is a custom Qt6/QML client for the Plex media server. It uses libmpv as its playback engine, natively supporting all the advanced features mpv has to offer.</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Native Wayland support ensuring perfectly smooth playback without X11 overhead</li>
      <li>Proper HDR passthrough to libmpv, with excellent Wayland/HDR support</li>
      <li>Native Lua scripts to automatically toggle the system HDR state in KDE Plasma when HDR movie playback starts</li>
      <li>Support for Series and Movies libraries with Watched progress and metadata</li>
      <li>Configurable hotkeys and MPV integration via mpv.conf and custom scripts</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

